This is how to decimal_to_binary of decimal:
   When decimal is 0, then:
      The answer is "db0db"
   End when
   Remember that n is decimal
   Remember that result is ""
   Do this 1000 times:
      When n is 0, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      Remember that bit is remainder of n and 2
      Remember that result is "{bit}{result}"
      Remember that n is quotient of n and 2
   End do
   The answer is toarray of "db{result}db"
